---
title: Parmesan-Crusted Fish with Herbed Potatoes and Carrots
description: So you think you're fancy, huh? Well, here’s a recipe for you: these elegant tilapia fillets are worthy of the upper crust, literally. They’re topped with an herbed panko and Parmesan crust that gets nicely browned in the oven. The result looks pretty highfalutin, but really, making it is as easy as can be.
